WEBVTT

00:07:31.326 --> 00:07:32.980
AdG: The problem is burnout.

00:07:33.596 --> 00:07:36.496
Sure, it's exhausting to deal
with rude customers all day.

00:07:37.006 --> 00:07:40.415
But how exhausting, depends on the way
you approach emotional labor.

00:07:40.863 --> 00:07:44.314
There's substantial evidence
that people who do a lot of surface acting

00:07:44.338 --> 00:07:47.379
end up feeling more
emotionally drained and stressed.

00:07:47.403 --> 00:07:51.212
AlG: The more we surface act,
the more we're likely to drink.

00:07:51.236 --> 00:07:56.461
It also is linked to not helping out
as much at home, because you're exhausted.

00:07:56.485 --> 00:07:58.867
So, there's a lot of potential downsides.

00:07:58.891 --> 00:08:02.184
AdG: But there's an alternative
to surface acting --